eligibility_criteria.description:
Minimum age: 40 Years
Maximum age: 60 Years
This trial does not accept healthy volunteers.
Peripheral neuropathy >= grade 3, according to Common Terminology Criteria for Adverse Events (CTCAE), version 3.0
Willing and able to consent for biopsy of locally-advanced or metastatic breast cancer prior to treatment
Widespread progressive disease, i.e., more than 3 sites of progressive disease (more than 3 sites of disease are permitted provided there are no more than 3 sites of progressive disease)
Grade 3-4 electrolyte abnormalities (Common Terminology Criteria for Adverse Events [CTCAE], version [v.] 4):
Aspartate aminotransferase (AST) or alanine aminotransferase (ALT) < 3 x institutional ULN within 14 days prior to registration

Patients with stable brain metastases are eligible for this trial. However, patients
             must not have required steroid treatment for their brain metastases within 30 days of
             Screening.
Patients with malignant pleural or pericardial effusions are not eligible

outcome_measures.measure: To characterize the safety and tolerability of elesclomol sodium administered once weekly to subjects with solid tumors

outcome_measures.time_frame: Cycle 1: multiple timepoints. Thereafter, single samples at designated cycles

outcome_measures.analysis_method: Induction: pre-infusion (0 hr) on Day 1 of Cycle 1; pre-infusion (within 5 hr prior to dose) on Day 1 on Cycles 2, 4; Post-induction: at treatment discontinuation (up to Month 24); 120 days and 1-2 years post-last dose (maximum up to 5 years) (infusion duration: 90 minutes) (1 cycle: 21 days)
outcome_measures.time_frame: Pre-infusion (0 hr) on Day 1 of Cycle 1 up to maximum 5 years. Detailed timeframe is given in outcome measure description.

outcome_measures.analysis_method: The ORR will be computed for subjects with tumors of secondary interest which include the following 4 tumor types Osteosarcoma, Neuroblastoma (measurable), Neuroblastoma (evaluable), and Hepatoblastoma.
outcome_measures.measure: The investigator assessed ORR for the tumor types of secondary interest.
outcome_measures.time_frame: Primary analysis perform 20 weeks after LPFV in the 3 cohorts of primary interest
